# P3.2 differential corpus — derived flux streams.
#
# gen_corpus.py writes the gw-converted .scp files here. They are a
# BUILD ARTIFACT, regenerated on demand from corpus/sources/*:
#   - ~133 MB total for the 6-format corpus (not repo-suitable)
#   - gw's .scp header carries a non-deterministic timestamp (no stable
#     hash) — the flux *data* is deterministic, which is all the
#     differential needs (it compares decoded sectors, not .scp bytes)
#
# The committed, deterministic, hash-manifested corpus is
# corpus/sources/ + corpus/MANIFEST.sha256. Run gen_corpus.py to
# (re)populate this directory.
*
!.gitignore
